{"tid":239110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 問題不在「連登神探」 「口德撚」「冷血撚」「有人炒車」","createTime":"2017-05-11T12:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T15:12:00.000Z","uid":34869,"like":31,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"efa1fae2e31276147b1f7303c3f82e02f71f5061","tid":239110,"uid":34869,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而係有班判官周圍辣火頭開post洗版</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不論高登連登, 有post討論就有唔同人入去留言, 所謂既例如「所以女人都係雞」一直都係個別人士既立場, 而都一直有人叫人「收下把死人口」。<br />\n<br />\n而神探系列又係一有奇案就有, 以前藍可兒case係, 智障肥仔被屈都係, 有咩論點唔同既就響個post入面解決。<br />\n<br />\n但係近排有班哪來的判官:<br />\n<br />\n見到個post入面有人話人係雞, 就係咁出post話「連登仔眼中個個女人都係雞」<br />\n見到個post入面有人口臭, 就係咁出post話「連登變左冷血集中地」<br />\n見到個post入面有人收口, 就係咁出post話「連登變左口德撚集中地」<br />\n見到個post入面有人討論案情, 就係咁出post話「連登神探又炒車」 <br />\n<br />\n再重申, 唔同種類既人響高登連登一直都存在, 各個post入面既討論/罵戰一直都有, 一向都有人炒車有人冇炒, 但如今有一群人就抽個post一兩個人既言論洗被式出post玩審判, 呢班人總係以自己高人一等, 總之左中右既comment都係小學雞, 再加一句「d連登仔就係咁既質素」。<br />\n<br />\n依家呢班人就一日開十幾個post然後圍威喂推撚曬d垃圾審判post上頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞撚到好似連登全部都係引戰罵戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不如開個法院台比你地班仆街入面自high算鳩數啦好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb54be5cf1bb5074bf419fe0f7b113e7a1c360f","tid":239110,"uid":55043,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"我屌<br />\n<br />\n好彩仲有d心水清既會員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bad99d16b608e3fcf77c6e1e2e036c368b2667","tid":239110,"uid":38041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:39:36.000Z","msg":"吓？香港人愈嚟愈多人都話：「乜香港已經變成咁」然後若無其事過日子<br />\n<br />\n對比返連登 言行好一致呀 有咩問題先"},{"pid":"1902b6e885e1871569faef37e0faa54d06916abb","tid":239110,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:43:18.000Z","msg":"審判台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d484d76a05d4c9844a79480bfb0707a19c4312","tid":239110,"uid":24140,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/11/204444_5fad2d82f95e76e2b7a720456d5e3e5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F11%2F204444_5fad2d82f95e76e2b7a720456d5e3e5e.jpg&h=44c933c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bed5747221c8c9c8d2910171d7336be611efcfb","tid":239110,"uid":44562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:46:09.000Z","msg":"咁呢個 post 算唔算判官 post 呀又 ?"},{"pid":"f5e179d523db3ee328df0256b46297384d9435bb","tid":239110,"uid":60720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:47:45.000Z","msg":"你個POST唔會有人入嚟討論架<br />\n諗下點解"},{"pid":"8207d3293fdae2bb0b22c131250b684819251882","tid":239110,"uid":34869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吓？香港人愈嚟愈多人都話：「乜香港已經變成咁」然後若無其事過日子<br />\n<br />\n對比返連登 言行好一致呀 有咩問題先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n利申高登轉會, 高登連登一向都都有唔同意見<br />\n<br />\n高登果陣馬倬朗都係post內互片, 黎到連登其實冇變到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但點解依家係變成: 「依家連登d小學雞?」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8f160d321a09550105a8c62e4a9ece35d44270","tid":239110,"uid":52911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:50:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁呢個 post 算唔算判官 post 呀又 ?</blockquote><br />\n算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f544281d990540e11c68054616e8bc316a64f5d4","tid":239110,"uid":34869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2